K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-12: bdag po dang bcas pa'i dur khrod nas gos ma len cig /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-15: dur khrod nas shin tu mi ring ba zhig na log pa'i lha khang zhig yod de /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-16: de nas ras shig rlung gis khyer nas dur khrod du lhung ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-17: dge slong zhig phyag dar khrod kyi gos tshol zhing dur khrod du 'ongs pa des ras de rnyed nas de blangs te khyer ba dang /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-18: log pa'i lha khang na gnas pa de dag gis mthong nas btsun pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-19: bdag gi ras 'di log pa'i lha khang nas dur khrod du lhung ba yin gyi /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-22: de ste khyod kyi yin na /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:447b-24: dge slong de 'gyod pa skyes nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01acip-k_lha_sa-012-002:448a-1: yod med shin tu rtogs la longs shig ////
